es, it was - a tenement house. The landlady was a Mrs Bird and - her uncle was an engine driver and - when he retired they moved to Stanford-in-the-Vale, Berkshire, and then my mother took over the house and .....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Did you have any other relatives or lodgers living there?
