No, but he could make furniture. Oh, he made furniture - yes. In fact if it wasn't to dirty I'd - if it's not broke up I've got that - bit of that old - smoking cab
inet still out in the coal cellar. Oh, it's reckon it's smothered in coal - it's out there now if it's not broken up - I don't know.
