n her, she comes up every now and again, and we used to say - take this cup of tea into dad. You know what it used to be? Not }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7627976\charrsid11030117 vinegar}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
