}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 
 washing, and I can see it now with an old oil lamp and all the steam. There's mother scrubbing away there - yes. But I couldn't stand stand it when she used to use chloride lime. When she used it - oh - anyway I used t
