\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Could you bring toys or books to the table?
