Yes, we'd been to Richmond - places like that you know. Oh yes, any places of - Hampton Court - places of interest you know, you used to - oh yes, they used to take us about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 
No, I don't think I can say that. The only time I had a holiday was when the school was being done up and they sent me down to Stanford-in-the-Vale, Berkshire. When I got down there the people I stopped with sent me to school down there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Can you tell me how you spent Saturdays in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Oh we, we used to go to Sunday school. Oh yes, we always used to have to go to Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 In the morning or the afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 In the mornings, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 How long would that last?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 
I suppose about an hour - used to be about hour. Around St Clements church there. And we - church house - used to be a small church house then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 What about Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Oh, Saturday was a busy day for all of us. Shopping and cleaning and - oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Did you wear different clothes at the weekend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 If we had 'em. If they wasn't in the pawn shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Did you play any games at weekends?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Oh yes. Ordinary kiddies games - games that you never see now. Such as tippi-cat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7627976\charrsid11030117 What\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117  that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 
We used to sharpen a piece of wood, a point at each end, and you had a stick and you put it on the ground like that you see and you hit it. It'd jump up and you'd hit it and then you'd run - like cricket more or less, but that was tippi-cat. Yes, yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Your parents didn't think it was wrong to work or play on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Oh yes. Yes, they did, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 You weren't allowed to play at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 No, no. Only like indoors but never out in the street 
or anything like that. We could play as I say ordinary - ordinary games indoors. Draughts or anything like that but not - oh, no cards or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Did your parents attend any place of worship?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 When they were younger yes. Yes, they did. Later years they - they gave it up but they - they were proper churchgoers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 When you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 What denomination were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Er - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7627976\charrsid11030117 oh dear}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117  oh - Protestants.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 How often did they go to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Oh quite regular - quite regular.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Every Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Oh yes, quite regularly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Morning or evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 They used to go in the evening mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Your mother and father both together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Oh yes. They used to attend I think I previously said - at Field Lane Mission on Rosebery Avenue. Yes, that's where they used to go.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Did you go as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Did you go to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Yes, we went to Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Were there any Sunday school outings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Oh yes, we used to go - in the horse coaches years ago - to - Critic Wood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Where's that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 
Oh, I couldn't tell you now - another one they had just the other side of Barnet. I can't think of the name of them - Abbey Woods - Abbey Woods. Oh used to have - we used to have quite - l
ittle treats you know, all have a badge pinned on us and goodies given to us. Oh yes, it was quite nice.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Do you remember how often these outings took place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Oh, mostly once a year you see, yes. Once a year, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 What other social activities organized by the church did you take part in when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 
Sports - boxing and that. When they renewed the church house and made a big church house just round in St Clements Street there, yes, all sports there - boxing everything like that - fencing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 And you went along?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 I went along - I wasn't very much good at any of them but I used to - do me bit like. Yes, had a go, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Did you belong to the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Not to the church choir - no. The school choir, belonged to the school choir, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Did the church run any temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Well that was more or less the boys club. You, - what I was just referring to you see, that was more or less the same thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 That was a temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 And you were a member of that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Did you belong to any other club organized by the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 
Oh, I should say that they - our headmaster at school, he formed a church lads brigade round there and I was a member of that. Yes, Church Lads Brigade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 And what did you do in that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Used to play - a fife. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 What's a fife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Flute. A flute.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Were you good at it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Well - fairly, you know. I was in the band anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Was grace said at meals in your family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Oh yes. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Who said it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Father. Me father - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 No, I don't - no, I don't think we - not to that extent. Mother - mother always used to 
- fetch out pieces from the Bible you know but - we never had anything like you're referring to.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 But she would read pieces out of the Bible?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Oh yes. Yes. Oh, she knew her Bible - so did dad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Did your father take an interest in Politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Yes. Very much so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Do you know what his views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Conservative. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Why do you think he held those views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Well - I don't know actually, I was quite a youngster you see, but when he took an active part he was a great orator - he
 could speak when they used to have the meetings at street corners. You could hear his voice above anybody's. He - only a little man - I'll show you his photo in a mo - and he had a very powerful pair of lungs and he would be heard. He was a great orator.
 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Why do you think he chose to be Conservative rather than any of the others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 
Well, the two parties at that time as I can remember was - Liberal - two main - Liberal and Conservative. And I don't know whether it was the - oh no, he wouldn'
t he wouldn't have been influenced by anybody - he had his own mind. But - he was - he believed in - well, what the word means - conserving. He believed in saving - you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Did your mother take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Oh yes, she was Conservative and all, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Why do you think she was Conservative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Well, I - whether it was to follow dad or not I couldn't say - I suppose so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Do you remember your mother or father voting in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Oh yes. Oh yes. Oh, they never missed it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 And they voted Conservative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Yes. They never missed it, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 In some places at that }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7627976\charrsid11030117 time}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117  men felt that they risked losing their job or their house if they voted differently from their employers do you know if your father felt himself under that kind of pressure?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 
No, I don't think so because - actually his - his boss - well, he was more of a Red - more of a Red - oh yes - rank Socialist but more of a - I think my father used to refer him to as a anarchist.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 It didn't make any difference to your father's job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 
No. His name was Finimore. Name was Finimore and they had a - used to trade under the name of Wilmotts in the Caledonian Road - pianoforte shop - yes, that was their name.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Was your father actually a member of the Conservative party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Oh yes, yes.
