\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 You think he treated you well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Well - these two old ladies - yes, they were very good, yes.
