Well, of course in the shop - oh, all right. I used to get on very well they used to laugh because there used to be as much paint on me face as there was on the wheels by the time I'd finished for the day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 How did your employer treat you there?
