\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 And you were getting eight shillings a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Eight shillings a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Did you feel that was a fair wage?
