\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Oh, I liked it very much, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 After that in 1914 you joined up with the Territorials?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 And then you said you did something for one month?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 
For one month - from July 1914 to August - for one month - I was appointed as a carman at eighteen years of age. And then we went away to camp with the Territorials at Shoreham and - the war was declared and we went back t
o the London depot in Shaftesbury and from there we embarked to - to Waterloo and we went - finished up in Malta relieving the regulars.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 And you stayed in the Territorials 'til you were demobbed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392287\charrsid11030117 Demobbed - we went to France soon after our training at Malta - we went to France in the December 1914 and then I was demobbed in 1919.}
{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Since the end of the first world war you came back and went on the railways?
