\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 I did motor driving up 'til two years ago. Yes, 'til '67. I've got - thirty-six years }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16392287\charrsid11030117 safety }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 first driving awards - never had an accident so - 1930 I entered it - I didn't enter it before 1930 but I'll show you 'em before you go.
