\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Did you feel that there were divisions of interest among workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Oh yes, yes there was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11407999 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Some people say that in those days there was a great division between trained craftsmen and other workers - did you feel that or not?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16531778 HE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11226032\charrsid11030117 Yes, now then - that's a funny thing that happens - well, not quite so much today but a fe
